See `AGENTS.md` at the repository root for the main project guidance.

Key expectations for this repo:

- Keep business logic out of `PlannerRootView.swift` when possible.
- Route persisted settings through `AppSettings.swift`.
- Route planner mutations through `PlannerStore.swift`.
- Add or update tests when changing planner rules, carry-forward behavior, import/export, or audio-library logic.
- Run `swift test` before wrapping up when practical.
